[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     74[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ### Issue 5: `store_recommendation` Does Not Store `explanation` Field
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     75[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     76[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **File:** `chapter15.09-python-example.md`
