[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    103[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## Pseudocode vs. Python Consistency
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    104[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    105[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Overall good alignment. The Python implements the core flow from the main recipe's pseudocode (state extraction, policy query, safety check, explanation, clinician decision capture). Key differences:
