[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    135[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    136[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The opening disclaimer is well-placed and appropriately strong about this not being clinically validated. The Gap to Production section is thorough, covering physics accuracy, regulatory pathway, multi-site validation, and clinician trust.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    137[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
