[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    139[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    140[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## Logical Flow
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    141[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    142[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The code builds understanding in a natural progression:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    143[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 1. Config/constants (clinical knowledge encoded as numbers)
